{
  "stem": "13258.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Zuckerman-- ?] who was from the [INAUDIBLE] a sandwich I had mentioned once-- who was the chief distributor of those things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the reason he was helpful, because there came medication also with it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And with some of that medication, he bribed a Soviet minister who was in that town, transferred from Moscow, and the people at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The minister's wife was sick, and Dr.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Zuckerman ?] was called to help her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so that helped a little bit with the authorities in that town.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so until that help had arrived, we were absolutely miserable.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We lived for a long time in dormitories, where the only room you had was the room beneath your bed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The sanitary conditions were lousy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Food was scarce.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were swollen from hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I had frostbites on both hands.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "There was-- our clothing was torn by then already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So when the stuff came-- the Polish help came, it really-- we started to live a little bit better.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We also had, while we worked on the farm, stolen enough peas, while we were harvesting peas, to support us for a couple months with some additional food.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So that helped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But the Polish army, which had been created under General [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Anders, ?] soon left the Soviet Union during the Battle of Stalingrad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And besides, they had taken on only a limited number of Jews.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We found out, later on, why the Soviets had made that demand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "They had not specified Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They had specified other minorities and Poles, and they were afraid, mainly afraid, that people from the territories which they had occupied in 1939 from the [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Polish perimeter, ?] that Ukrainians and white Russians would try to join the Polish army in order to get rid of the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
